[style name="res://Dialogue/Styles/CozyPersonaVN.tres"]
[background arg="res://Art/Backgrounds/classroom.png" fade="0.7"]
The first day of the new term.
Students slowly fill the classroom. Some chat with friends while others scroll through their phones. The room buzzes with excitement and nervous energy.
Maya Ilagan (21), a Computer Science student, enters carrying her bag and several notebooks.
She scans the room.
A familiar voice calls out.
join Ethan (neutral) right [animation="Instant In"]
Ethan: Uy, Maya!
Maya turns.
Ethan Yap waves from his seat.
Maya smiles, relieved.
join Maya (neutral) left [animation="Instant In"]
Maya: Ethan!
She walks over and sits beside him.
Ethan: Long time no see ah.
Maya: Parang one sem lang naman.
Ethan: One sem is too long. It's still one sem.
Maya: Drama mo talaga.
Ethan: Musta naman?
update Maya (soft)
Maya sighs.
Maya: Okay lang siguro? Kinakabahan lang sa subjects this term kasi graduating na tayo. Oh! I did also see my favorite artist in this event I went too!
[signal arg="emotion:nervous"]
It. was. amazing.
update Ethan (glad)
Ethan brings out an encouraging smile.
Ethan: That sounds so fun! and Hey, normal lang 'yan Maya, I know kakayanin naman naten toh.
Maya nods, wanting to change the subject.
Maya: Eh Ikaw? Musta ka na?
Ethan: Mmm same old same old. Busy. Surviving.
Maya: Surviving daw. Ikaw nga lagi mataas grades.
Ethan: Grades don't make everything easy.
Maya: Wow. Sabagay.
The classroom begins settling down.
A Professor enters.
Everyone quickly returns to their seats.
join Professor (neutral) right [animation="Instant In"]
Professor: Good morning, class.
The class: Good morning, sir.
Professor: Since this is our first meeting, let's get to know each other first.
The professor writes on the board.
"What are your future dreams and goals?"
Professor: When I call your name, introduce yourself and tell us what you hope to achieve in the future.
Students begin introducing themselves.
One after another.
Some confidently talk about their future careers.
Others discuss plans abroad.
Maya listens quietly.
Each answer makes her uncertainty sink deeper into her thoughts.
Eventually...
Professor: Ethan Yap?
Ethan stands.
Ethan: Good morning everyone, nice to meet you all! I'm Ethan Yap.
He speaks naturally and confidently.
Ethan: After graduation, I want to work in software development and gain experience first. Hopefully someday makapag-start din ako ng sarili kong tech company.
Several students nod.
Professor: Ambitious but very good. May you go far.
The professor says with a smile
Ethan nods and sits.
Maya glances down at her notebook.
Professor: Next up is Maya Ilagan.
Maya freezes.
[signal arg="emotion:nervous"]
A few seconds pass.
The entire room waits.
Slowly, she stands.
Maya: Uh...
She grips her notebook tighter.
Maya: I'm Maya Ilagan.
The silence feels heavier.
Professor: And your future plans?
Maya searches for an answer.
Nothing comes.
Maya: Honestly po...
She swallows.
Maya: I haven't really thought about it yet.
A few students exchange glances.
The professor simply nods.
Professor: That's fine. Take your seat, Ms. Ilagan.
Maya sits down.
A moment of relief—
Yet somehow more uncertain than before.
She avoids eye contact for the rest of class.
leave Ethan [animation="Instant Out"]
leave Maya [animation="Instant Out"]
leave Professor [animation="Instant Out"]
[background arg="res://Art/Backgrounds/campus_hallway.png" fade="0.7"]
The lunch bell rings.
[signal arg="sfx:school_bell"]
Students pour out of classrooms.
Maya and Ethan walk together.
join Ethan (neutral) right [animation="Instant In"]
Ethan: Mukhang ninerbyos ka kanina ah.
join Maya (neutral) left [animation="Instant In"]
Maya: Ughhh, nooo... Super halata ba?
Maya asks nervously.
Ethan: Mmm medj.
update Ethan (glad)
Ethan grins.
Maya: Shucks nakaakahiya.
Ethan: Pshh, hindi naman. Lots of people don't know what to do in life.
Maya: ... But everyone had answers to what they want in their future.
Maya interjects.
Ethan: Hindi naman lahat... Trust me, maraming nagkukunwari lang.
update Maya (glad)
Maya just chuckles nervously.
Ethan: Pero real, okay ka lang ba?
update Ethan (frown)
Ethan shares a concerned look towards her and she sighs.
Maya: Yeah... I guess..
Maya: Actually... wait, no. Not really, I honestly don't know ano talaga gusto kong gawin and it feels like I'm stuck.
Ethan: And that's okay, as I've said a lot of people don't know what to do in life
Maya: 'Bat parang hindi.
Ethan: Maya, we're in our twenties. Hindi naman kailangan alam mo agad lahat.
Maya's expression becomes more neutral and solemn.
Maya: Edi sana ganyan din tingin ng parents ko.
Ethan notices the seriousness in her voice.
Ethan: Are things okay at home? You know you can always tell me.
update Maya (soft)
Maya sighs.
Maya: Everythings okay naman.
A pause.
Maya: Just... a lot of expectations placed on my lap now.
Ethan: Yikes,gets kita jan.
Maya notices Ethan looking away.
Maya: Ikaw?
Ethan: Huh?
Maya: May problema ka rin ba? Seems like something on your mind?
Ethan hesitates.
Ethan: ... Medyo meron.
Maya: What happened?
Ethan: Just family stuff.
Ethan waves his hand around like it's nothing.
Maya waits patiently.
Ethan: Mom and Dad aren't...really doing great right now.
Maya: Oh gosh, I'm so sorry to hear that...
Ethan: It's okay, It's fine. It's not that big of a deal.
Maya: No, Ethan seriously, this is a hard thing to experience.
update Maya (frown)
Maya frowns and shows her concern.
Ethan: Ehh we'll figure it out, we always do naman. It shouldn't take that much of a toll on us... I suppose?
Maya: Hey, Still. Ethan if you ever need someone to talk to...
Ethan: I know Maya, it's okay.
He smiles tightly.
Ethan: Thanks for your support. It means a lot.
The two continue walking.
For a moment, neither of them feels completely alone.
[signal arg="emotion:lost"]
leave Ethan [animation="Instant Out"]
leave Maya [animation="Instant Out"]
[background arg="res://Mocks/Novel UI/image 3.png" fade="0.7"]
Dinner.
The family sits around the table.
Ricardo Ilagan has just returned from work.
His demeanor is tired but gives a half hello.
Jennifer greets him excitedly but is stopped from her husband.
She gets an earful sayin how tired he is.
Not now.
Next time.
Jennifer slowly nods and gives a small smile.
She understands
Jennifer decided to scroll through social media while eating.
She notes that Maya is also exhausted from studying, she eats her meal whilst watching youtube.
join Ricardo (neutral) right [animation="Instant In"]
Ricardo: Alam mo, Maya.
Maya looks up.
Ricardo: Yung anak ng katrabaho ko, graduate na.
join Maya (neutral) left [animation="Instant In"]
Maya: Ohhh talaga po?
Ricardo: Oo.
Jennifer immediately joins the conversation.
join Jennifer (neutral) right [animation="Instant In"]
Jennifer: Yes anak, alam mo may trabaho na rin sya agad.
Ricardo: Mhm tama.
update Jennifer (glad)
Jennifer smiles.
Jennifer: Malapit ka na rin grumaduate kaya ikaw naman next.
update Maya (smile)
Maya forces a smile.
Maya: Hopefully po-
Ricardo cuts Maya off.
Ricardo: Aba syempre, before you know it you'll have your very own job.
Jennifer: Eto Maya tingnan mo, marami na rin akong nakikitang opportunities abroad.
She taps her phone and puts it right in front of her face.
Jennifer: Padala ko sayo mamaya ha Diba maganda toh Ric?
Ricardo nods but doesnt say anything.
Maya's smile weakens but nods nonetheless.
Maya: Sige lang po.
Ricardo: Basta mag focus lang sa classes mo ha.
Maya: Yes po Tay.
Jennifer looks up from her phone and studies her daughter.
Jennifer: Kumusta nga pala grades mo?
Maya freezes.
[signal arg="emotion:nervous"]
Only slightly.
But enough.
Her gaze is fixed on her phone, too unsure of what to say next.
Jennifer furrows her brows,her silence is mistaken as indiference.
As if Maya would rather be anywhere else than answer her.
Jennifer: Okay naman?
Maya: Uh...
She forces herself to stay calm. The grip on her phone tightens.
