Exam day.
The family eats breakfast together.
Ricardo quietly skims through paperwork for the auto repair shop while finishing his coffee.
Jennifer packs Maya's lunch and mentally goes over the day's errands.
Meanwhile...
The knot in her stomach only loosens when she checks her phone.
Anything to keep from thinking about the exam waiting for her.
Maya scrolls through messages beneath the table.
A notification appears.
