	Maya sprints through the campus.
	Students are already leaving the examination building.
	Some laugh.
	Others discuss the exam.
	Maya slows down.
	Confused.
	Then...
	Her eyes widen.
	She looks at the time.
	Then toward the classroom.
	No.
